text: Jorge Hugo Rojas Justiniano (born 6 December 1993) is a Bolivian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Always Ready. ==International career== Rojas made his senior debut for the Bolivia national football team in a 2-2 friendly tie with Nicaragua on 3 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Santa Cruz de la Sierra Category:Bolivian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Sport Boys Warnes players Category:Club Always Ready players Category:Bolivian Primera División players Category:Bolivia international footballers
title: Jorge Rojas (Bolivian footballer)
